# InterVue Labs - Cursor Guide

## What This Is

AI-powered interview simulator. Conducts intelligent, conversational interviews with real-time voice. Adapts questions based on answers, detects contradictions, remembers context ‚Äî feels like talking to a real interviewer.

**Current Branch:** `04-05-26-fine-tuning-project` *(verify locally)*
**Current State:** Phase 1C COMPLETE. Sessions 1‚Äì3 arena fixes implemented (VAD, silence flow, presence monitor, unified TTS). **Manual re-test checklist in `testing_log.md`** before Phase 1D.

---

## Tech Stack

**Backend:** FastAPI (Python 3.11+), Supabase (PostgreSQL), SQLModel, JWT auth
**AI:** OpenAI GPT-4o-mini (LLM), OpenAI TTS, `gpt-4o-transcribe` (whisper-1 fallback), `text-embedding-3-small` (1536-dim embeddings)
**Frontend:** React 19, Vite 7, Tailwind CSS v3, Radix/shadcn UI, Lucide React, Framer Motion

