## Core Interview Flow

```
AI plays question audio (TTS via OpenAI)
    ‚Üì
Audio queue ends ‚Üí auto-listen starts (Silero VAD on recording stream)
    ‚Üì
12s dead-silence detector (Silero ‚Äî not FFT energy)
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ User speaks within 12s
    ‚îÇ       ‚Üì  speech detected
    ‚îÇ   Recording in progress (waveform bars animate)
    ‚îÇ       ‚Üì  5s of silence after speech ends
    ‚îÇ   Auto-submit ‚Äî no button press needed
    ‚îÇ       ‚Üì
    ‚îÇ   POST /api/interview/submit-answer-realtime
    ‚îÇ       ‚Üì
    ‚îÇ   Orchestrator ‚Üí Decision Engine ‚Üí TTS ‚Üí buildAudioQueue(isFollowUp)
    ‚îÇ       ‚Üì
    ‚îÇ   GlowingOrb pulses ‚Üí audio ends ‚Üí auto-listen restarts
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îî‚îÄ No speech for 12s
            ‚Üì
        LLM rephrase (text on screen + TTS) ‚Üí fresh 12s listen window
            ‚Üì  still silent
        Motivation TTS only (no banner text) ‚Üí skip submit ‚Üí next question
            ‚Üì  3 consecutive silent skips
        Wrap-up TTS ‚Üí Feedback

Parallel: Video presence monitor (from Start Interview ‚Üí end)
    3s out of frame ‚Üí warning TTS + banner, clock resets
    10s still out ‚Üí countdown ‚Üí wrap-up ‚Üí Feedback
    Return to frame ‚Üí resume listening (see presenceMonitor.js)
```

> **Audio bus:** Only one interviewer clip at a time. `stopAllAIAudio()` + `interviewActiveRef`. Presence warnings defer if question/motivation is playing. Never set `interviewActiveRef = false` in `releaseAllMedia()` ‚Äî only on explicit end.

